Aarav's form is sending nothing to the server. Find the bug:<br><pre><code>&lt;form action="/submit" method="POST"&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" id="username"&gt;
  &lt;button type="submit"&gt;Go&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>

Ananya's form has a file upload that never sends the file. Fix:<br><pre><code>&lt;form action="/upload" method="POST"&gt;
  &lt;input type="file" name="pic"&gt;
  &lt;button type="submit"&gt;Upload&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>
